19
00:02:43,290 --> 00:02:44,340
You don't need to ask my permission.

20
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:45,670
I'm not the house owner.

21
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:48,210
Since we're roommates,

22
00:02:48,860 --> 00:02:50,790
