what do you want?

25
00:03:01,780 --> 00:03:03,860
I just want to have an informal dinner with you.

26
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:04,950
An informal dinner?

27
00:03:04,950 --> 00:03:06,810
You call this an informal dinner?

28
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,270
I don't believe you would be so nice to me

29
00:03:09,270 --> 00:03:10,070
